description: Try our easy to follow Veggie Packed Mac & Cheese recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Veggie Packed Mac & Cheese Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 400 g no added salt cannellini beans

recipeInstructions.text: Spray a 2L baking dish lightly with olive oil and pour in the vegetable and bean mixture. Top with remaining beans and cheese and bake for 20 minutes until golden on top.
